<p>Welcome to the HARMAN Professional Marketing Toolkit!</p>

<p>To confirm the account, either click the link below or forward
	this message to the new user.</p>

<p><b>New User Details:</b></p>
<p>Name: <%= @resource.name %><br/>
	Email: <%= @resource.email %></p>

<p>You can confirm your account by clicking the link below:</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Confirm account',
  confirmation_url(
    @resource,
    confirmation_token: @token,
    host: @resource.respond_to?(:last_host) && @resource.last_host.present? ? @resource.last_host : UserMailer.default_url_options[:host]
  ) %></p>
